Milton C. Lightner (1949–1958)
Donald P. Kircher (1958–1975)
Joseph Bernard Flavin (1975–1987)
Paul Bilzerian (1987–1989)[21]
Iftikhar Ahmed (1989–1997)[22]
Stephen H. Goodman (1998–2004)

